(9, 'Intimate French Dining in Greenwich Village', 'MIMI is a cozy French bistro nestled in New York City''s Greenwich Village. The restaurant offers a charming ambiance reminiscent of classic Parisian eateries. The menu features traditional French dishes with a modern twist, such as the notable Riz Noirâ€”a black squid ink risotto topped with grilled squid and shavings of bottarga. The roast chicken is also a reliable choice, known for its moist and flavorful preparation. While the space is intimate, which can lead to a bustling atmosphere, the attentive service and culinary delights make it a worthwhile dining experience for those seeking authentic French cuisine in the heart of Manhattan.', '2024-07-24', ST_PointFromText('POINT(40.72837218315401 -74.0006565061417)', 4326), '185 Sullivan St, New York, NY 10012', 'ChIJQW1zApJZwokRKDxrWkdKo5c', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Mimi_%28New_York_City_restaurant%29_%E2%80%93_January_2023_%E2%80%93_by_MainlyTwelve.jpg/1280px-Mimi_%28New_York_City_restaurant%29_%E2%80%93_January_2023_%E2%80%93_by_MainlyTwelve.jpg', 1, 5, 6, '2024-07-10 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(10, 'A Must-See for History and Military Enthusiasts', 'The Intrepid Sea, Air & Space Museum is an unforgettable experience, offering visitors the chance to explore a real aircraft carrier, historic fighter jets, a space shuttle, and even a submarine. The interactive exhibits bring military and aviation history to life, making it a great destination for both adults and kids. Walking through the massive USS Intrepid and standing beneath the Space Shuttle Enterprise is awe-inspiring. Whether you''re passionate about history, technology, or just looking for a unique NYC attraction, this museum is well worth a visit.', '2025-02-23', ST_PointFromText('POINT(40.76490244641803 -74.00083596515348)', 4326), 'Pier 86, W 46th St, New York, NY 10036', 'ChIJnxlg1U5YwokR8T90UrZiIwI', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Intrepid_Museum_%2849052290092%29.jpg/1280px-Intrepid_Museum_%2849052290092%29.jpg', 15, 72, 2, '2025-02-25 21:51:05.000000', '2025-02-25 21:51:05.000000', NULL),
(11, 'An Engaging and Family-Friendly Aquarium Experience', 'The Seattle Aquarium offers a fascinating glimpse into marine life, with exhibits showcasing the diverse ecosystem of the Pacific Northwest. Highlights include the underwater dome with 360-degree views of local sea life, playful sea otters, and the touch pools where visitors can interact with starfish and sea anemones. The aquarium is well-maintained, educational, and great for families with kids. While itâ€™s not the largest aquarium, the engaging exhibits and friendly staff make it a worthwhile visit for anyone interested in marine conservation and ocean life.', '2025-03-01', ST_PointFromText('POINT(47.60739929597848 -122.34295649612991)', 4326), '1483 Alaskan Way Pier 59, Seattle, WA 98101', 'ChIJQ_oEiK1qkFQRg3bU4l3mmWs', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b3/The_Seattle_Aquarium%E2%80%99s_Window_on_Washington_Water_exhibit_dive_show.jpg/1280px-The_Seattle_Aquarium%E2%80%99s_Window_on_Washington_Water_exhibit_dive_show.jpg', 0, 0, 4, '2025-03-02 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(12, 'A Lush Paradise for Nature Lovers', 'Fairchild Tropical Botanic Garden is a breathtaking escape into a world of rare and exotic plants. Located in Coral Gables, Florida, this 83-acre garden features stunning landscapes, winding pathways, and vibrant collections of tropical flora. Visitors can explore lush rainforests, serene butterfly gardens, and even a massive collection of palms and cycads. The garden is beautifully maintained, offering both relaxation and education through guided tours and seasonal events. Whether you''re a botany enthusiast or just looking for a peaceful retreat, Fairchild is a must-visit gem.', '2024-08-12', ST_PointFromText('POINT(25.67679087828212 -80.27203802454832)', 4326), 'Old Cutler Rd, Coral Gables, FL 33156', 'ChIJu_e4BnTI2YgREAOg3GxMK8g', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c7/Bailey_Palm_Glade_%285752321428%29.jpg/1280px-Bailey_Palm_Glade_%285752321428%29.jpg', 5, 19, 7, '2024-08-23 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
